		<title>York U Libraries join network of ‘open rangers’ to advance open educational resources</title>
		<link>https://www.library.yorku.ca/web/blog/2023/11/02/york-u-libraries-join-network-of-open-rangers-to-advance-open-educational-resources/?lang=fr</link>
		
